summary: This is an email chain between FBI personnel regarding a subpoena for L.S.J., LLC, a Delaware corporation identified as an Epstein entity that previously owned his private island before transferring it to another Epstein entity, Nautilus Inc. The email includes an attached subpoena and identifies the entity's address in the US Virgin Islands.

events.title: Subpoena Issued for L.S.J., LLC
events.description: An FBI financial investigator sends an email with an attached subpoena for L.S.J., LLC, a Delaware corporation linked to Jeffrey Epstein.

locations: 6100 Red Hook Quarter, Suite B-3, St Thomas, USVI 00802
keyFacts: L.S.J., LLC is identified as a Jeffrey Epstein entity.
L.S.J., LLC previously owned Epstein's private island before conveying it to Nautilus Inc, another Epstein entity.
L.S.J., LLC is a Delaware corporation but uses a business address in St. Thomas, US Virgin Islands.
The FBI's C-40 (FAST) squad, specifically a Senior Financial Investigator, was involved in issuing a subpoena to this entity in August 2019.
